data.description: New Beginnings, No Rent or Maintenance Fees. Welcome Home to Your Beautifully Updated and Maintained Home Boasting Two Bedrooms, One Full Bathroom. The Master is a Nice Size with Large WIC Complete with California Design Organizer, Enjoy the Kitchen with Beautiful Wood Cabinets, Granite Countertops, SS Appliances, Pantry, and Tile Floor. The Bathroom is Large and Tastefully updated, Hardwood Floors & Recessed Lighting Throughout. Gas Furnace & Hot Water Heater (2017) Three Storage Sheds on the Property, Roof and Siding (2012). Put this Gem on Your Must See List!
